EMAIL: mattsplace@sbcglobal.net WEBSITE: www.tangodelta.org

Counter-Terrorist: Pretend this is a game of paintball, but you have
only one life. Don't waste it, and take tactics to eliminate the
opposing team. Stay in groups, and plan your attack carefully.
You should come out with a victory.

Terrorist: Eliminate the opposing team, and you shall go on to
be the most recognized paintballer team in the world. Watch your backs
and make sure you don't get caught up in the middle of a firefight.
Use smoke grenades to cover yourself while moving.

Tips and Advice: Take the water level (level 1) to get around to
the other side quicker. Shoot people you see above the grates, and
smoke areas that are needed. Have half of your people stay back,
and the other half rush spread out. Make sure you have all corners
covered, and this shall be an easy victory.

Heres a great map for all you HE-map FANS out there.  Heres the scoop.

The T's start on one side of the top level (behind breakable, but tough boxes) and the CT's start on the other side.  It begins by lobbing grenades found at your spawn to the other side of the level,  but turns into much more than that.  In the middle of the level is a line of m4s that you can get if you can dodge the grenades.  You cannot get to the other teams side unless you go through the underground tunnel, which has shotguns.  This battling goes from fun to an extraordinary barking wild good time as you can turn out the lights and dim them making it dark for a few seconds and then you can turn them back on again. on each side of the level are two red buttons which when shot trigger the lights. Its a VERY FUN and EXCITING map.   Props to the = HcO = clan for another great addition to their map cycle.    

If you wanna play this and other many exciting custom maps,  got to "= HcO =  Hot Cups of Ownage" server and have fun.  

DOWNLAOD IT !!   YOULL LIKE IT!!!

This is an arena out in the middle of no where. Competive teams teleport from the ships to the arena and commense battle. The teams are locked in the teleport room which has an afk/camper fail-safe system. The glass is a special high density glass that does not crack or shatter due to bullet strike, uneven pressure, and subzero temperatures. The floor has the latest artifical gravity technology giving earth-like gravity evenly over the etire surface. This might make an okay place for a death match; however the fail-safe system will still activate, although it will only do so once. Please enjoy this enjoy this map, and dont forget your vaccume suits. :P

Please see the README for additional information about the sky textures

An arena like 32 player map. As you might have guessed the map is in the sky...

Instead of buyzones you start with a knife and a pistol with 24 rounds (glock for T, usp for CT) and you'll then have to pick up more weapons (there's plenty of 'em scattered across the map) unless you want to run out of bullets. You may have to rely on your knife from time to time when that happens though. 

There are 12 pump-action shotguns (m3) and 12 Uzis (tmp, mac 10) in each spawn aswell.

There's atleast one of each weapon and grenade in the level except for that there is no AWP or semi-auto sniper rifles.

All the boxes seen in the screens are fully destructible and they'll have physics, with  few exceptions, and there're some traps, teleporters and hidden areas in the level aswell.

Don't forget to RATE the map, and plz send feedback if there's something you want fixed or improved.

Enjoy...
